title: Person in Manual Wheelchair Facing Right

verbs: Depicts using a manual wheelchair to move or navigate.
nouns: A person seated in a manual wheelchair facing to the right.

description: A person using a manual wheelchair and facing right. Represents accessibility, mobility, independence, or inclusion for people who use wheelchairs.
apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, the person in manual wheelchair facing right emoji shows a person seated in a manual wheelchair moving toward the right. The design emphasizes inclusion and accessibility, often symbolizing independence and freedom of movement.
